    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xiaoxibob/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">教子</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-10-02"
      class="main-meta">2011-10-02 12:19:10</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5117329_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                          战略是一门关于行动的艺术，也是一门关于权衡的艺术。这本书就是战略家的一本“葵花宝典”。为何说是葵花宝典呢？因为葵花宝典里的那句“欲练此功，必先自宫”的话也适用于这门艺术。那是男人最值得骄傲的地方所在，同样，对于战略家来说，他最骄傲的就是他的战略眼光...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5117329_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5117329_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










